<div class="container">
  <h2>How It Works</h2>
  <div class="cards mt-5">
    <div class="card-category" style="width: 22rem;">
      <div class="card-body">
        <i class="fas fa-map-marked-alt"></i>
        <h3 class="card-title">Find</h3>
        <p class="card-text">We give you access to every registered building site on our database, which you can filter based on location, pay, project duration and more.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="card-category" style="width: 22rem;">
      <div class="card-body">
        <i class="fas fa-check"></i>
        <h3 class="card-title">Confirm</h3>
        <p class="card-text">Confirm with a click of a button. Some sites will require an application to prove you have the necessary skills.</p>
        </div>
    </div>
    <div class="card-category" style="width: 22rem;">
      <div class="card-body">
        <i class="far fa-comments"></i>
        <h3 class="card-title">Messaging</h3>
        <p class="card-text">Bild has an in-built multi purpose messaging platform that will keep you up to date once you're job is confirmed.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>
